{
  "texts": [
    "The BPE text compression method is also reversible and lossless.",
    "The reversible property assures that the method can translate the symbolized token sequence back to the natural language of words.",
    "Lossless in the sense of compression methods means that there is no loss of information during the compression that will lead to ambiguity during the decompression.",
    "A token embedding method converts the token symbols to number vectors that a computer can use to represent tokens in a computational number space.",
    "A desirable feature of token embedding is to reflect the position of the token in the vocabulary for lookup."
  ]
}